{"tid":522803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得討論明星既時候，好多時都混淆左 正 同 靚 兩個concept","createTime":"2018-01-08T01:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T02:28:47.000Z","uid":126507,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55b77e6bd5953eb9a4bdb0dda483cb708423f72d","tid":522803,"uid":126507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:38:05.000Z","msg":"舉兩個例子，我知有d人可能會唔同意，唔好貼評女子相片潮文先<br />\n<br />\n我用我既眼光做例子，歡迎大家自己用返自己既眼光做例子，一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n首先係ali<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/497240/xlarge/8e4ed2c67d80dc0d3f39b38b8bd75b7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F497240%2Fxlarge%2F8e4ed2c67d80dc0d3f39b38b8bd75b7f.jpg&h=0406148d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/497242/xlarge/0a179e38a69dad3a2caf79d2e3a0dad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F497242%2Fxlarge%2F0a179e38a69dad3a2caf79d2e3a0dad4.jpg&h=1e9b292a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係普通人入面絕對係中上級別，如果係街到見到絕對會望多兩眼<br />\n<br />\n但佢面算大，五官平又唔係突出，係明星黎講其實一般<br />\n<br />\n應該就未到&ldquo;未見過咁靚既女&rdquo;既level<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://web-ss.b0.upaiyun.com/article/images/20171216/new/1513434502902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb-ss.b0.upaiyun.com%2Farticle%2Fimages%2F20171216%2Fnew%2F1513434502902.jpg&h=e951323d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/923011/xlarge/65d5c3aee8c4c16ecaebde77605d94db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F923011%2Fxlarge%2F65d5c3aee8c4c16ecaebde77605d94db.jpg&h=0eda89a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果你話&ldquo;未見過咁正既女&rdquo; 我同意既<br />\n<br />\n第二就係momo啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://miner8.com/en/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/momo-e1480684694628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fminer8.com%2Fen%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fmomo-e1480684694628.jpg&h=67d92ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/86/41/68/86416877aa62cf37a6df225dbc68374f--pretty-people-beautiful-people.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F86%2F41%2F68%2F86416877aa62cf37a6df225dbc68374f--pretty-people-beautiful-people.jpg&h=8d616cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔多講，意思都係同ali 差唔多，佢五官黎講唔算靚<br />\n<br />\n但佢跳舞即刻變到世界級既&ldquo;正&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s480x480/e15/c0.90.720.720/13597532_1088978797862272_1850885903_n.jpg?ig_cache_key=MTI4OTIxNjA0MDI4NjM5NjQ1OA%3D%3D.2.c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs480x480%2Fe15%2Fc0.90.720.720%2F13597532_1088978797862272_1850885903_n.jpg%3Fig_cache_key%3DMTI4OTIxNjA0MDI4NjM5NjQ1OA%253D%253D.2.c&h=db44db56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"312c46ec57c67062260ef7be7378deb276c6d0b1","tid":522803,"uid":126507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b81b4d05a1f89195eb9066b99b34864406027c4","tid":522803,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"Agger momo"}]}